title: Spyder Auto Installation: 2008-10 Jeep Grand Cherokee Bull Bar
description:
This video features a walkthrough of how to install a Spyder Auto Bull Bar on 2008-10 Jeep Grand Cherokee models. This video will guide you through the process of how to install the step bars and offers other helpful tips throughout to facilitate a successful installation.

Crafted from high quality steel.
-3 inch diameter steel tubing.
- Includes all mounting hardware and direct bolt-on with no drilling required.
- Support over 400 lbs.
- Installation instruction included.
